  "keyFeatures": [
    "Procedural DFS maze generation with perfect and imperfect modes",
    "BFS shortest-path solving algorithm",
    "Mandatory '42' pattern constraint stamp for grids >= 9x7",
    "Interactive ANSI-colored ASCII terminal visualization with animation",
    "Configuration-file-driven setup (KEY=VALUE format)",
    "Reusable mazegen Python package (distributable as .whl)",
    "Hexadecimal output file serialization of maze grid and solution path",
    "Multiple color palette cycling and real-time keyboard interaction"
